@rhtyd  All the failures due to the following error 
errorCode: 431, errorText:The VLAN tag vlan://846 is already being used for dynamic vlan allocation for the guest network in zone pr2311-t1646-kvm-centos7
This is not related to these code changes. Most likely cleanup issues in test code.  Any idea on the fixes related to this in test cases?

@sateesh-chodapuneedi @priyankparihar I've refactored the code to attempt disk resize only when user has explicitly provided a `rootdisksize` option. This prevents exceptions when the global setting for the full clone setting is false and this option is not provided.
@rafaelweingartner I've also added a null check based on your review, in the above vmware related code.

I'll now kick another round of smoke tests, remove old tests results/clutter.
